Dear friends, happy Saturday!
The weather wasn't cooperative last week, but we flew today anyway.
We practiced powered stall recovery, unpowered stall recovery, slow flight, simulated engine failure (!), route training, and landed three times with the help of our instructor, including one takeoff and landing.
Everything is good ^_^
